messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
I don't know what happened.
What is your name?
I'm down, what do I do?
What's wrong? Can you tell me what's going on?
You know what, I just killed all these people, and you don't know why.
You killed who? Can you tell me more?
You know what, I'm trying to get him.
You stupid bitch.
I'm calling you and I'm telling you.
You're not stupid. Can you tell me where you are?
I just told you. They are here with me.
I'm trying to stop this.
People are police. It's over.
And my way up here already.
Sir, you're talking fast.
Please don't let me kill myself.
Sir, I'm here to help. Tell me where you are.
I will come out if I know the police are not there.
I'm going to kill myself.
Please don't. We can work this out. Just tell me where you are.
I'm going out there with guns.
Just put the gun down, and tell me what you want me to do.
I'm not playing around. If they do anything, I'm going to kill myself.
Okay, let me know you're coming out, and I'll tell them.
Just make sure they don't kill me.
Sir, come out slowly with your hands up.
I'm going out with the gun on my chin. I won't do anything.
Just come out with your hands up and nothing in them. They have been notified you're coming out.
I'm coming out now.
You do not need to take your clothes off.
I just killed all these people. I'm done.
Sir, you're coming out now, right?
Yes, I'm trying. Please don't let me kill myself.
Put the gun down and walk to the front door.
Okay, I'm on my way.
Stay on the phone with me.
I'm in compliance.
Just stay right there. They'll let you know when to move.
If I see police, I'm going to kill myself. Let me know now.
